ions visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIImage"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"by the map view.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"title":"MapLibre","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"}}}